I need to identify the line items and values related to accrued interest that has not yet been received.

Looking at the balance sheet, I can see an account called "Interest Receivable" which represents interest that has been earned but not yet received. This is exactly what the task is asking for.

From the data provided:
- The initial value of "Interest Receivable" as of 2023-12-31 is 0.00
- The end value of "Interest Receivable" as of 2024-02-05 is 9881.70

This increase indicates that during this period, the company accrued interest of 9881.70 that had not yet been received by the end date.
